data.actual_result: Sound notification is not given to user, when they join a voice channel.
data.expected_result: Notification sound prompting user that they joined voice channel, helps when user joins accidentally.
data.short_description: Discord Canary, does not notify the user that they have joined a new servers voice channel.
data.steps_to_repro: - Create a server or join a server or go to existing server- If user creates a server, they will automatically join voice channel, else user goes to existing server and joins voice channel-
